This package ports source files from the appflowy_board package
(https://github.com/AppFlowy-IO/appflowy-board), originally licensed
under MPL-2.0 / AGPL-3.0 dual. manyui_board re-licenses those files
under MPL-2.0 only, retaining attribution to AppFlowy contributors.

The full MPL-2.0 text is available at:
https://www.mozilla.org/en-US/MPL/2.0/

MPL-2.0 is file-level copyleft: modifications to MPL-licensed files
must be released under MPL-2.0, but the rest of the manyui workspace
(MIT) is unaffected.
